Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.25,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:337830,340250}You're that Inokuma Daigo?{NOTE:じゃ、御前はあの猪野熊大悟か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:42.38,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:341170,342380}So you knew?{NOTE:知っていたのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.18,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:345260,347180}I've only heard the name.{NOTE:名前だけは聞いていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:54.22,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:347180,354220}And that Inokuma advanced an unnamed North Korean team to the world championship.{NOTE:無名の北朝鮮バレーボールチームを世界選手権にまで進めたコーチ陣に猪野熊と言う日本人がいたことはな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:06:00.23,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:356520,360230}Also that he was recently called back to Japan.{NOTE:それに、最近日本へ呼び戻されたと言う事もな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.94,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:360690,361940}I see.{NOTE:そうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.61,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:361940,363610}What are your plans now?{NOTE:これから何をするんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.07,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:365780,367070}I'm not sure yet.{NOTE:それは未だ分からん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.53,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:367070,369530}But I am a man who can't do anything but volleyball.{NOTE:しかし俺はバレーしか出来ない男だからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.00,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:372740,375000}How is your right arm?{NOTE:右手は未だ行けないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.54,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:375000,377540}It's completely useless now.{NOTE:すっかり駄目に成ってしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.04,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:377540,379040}I can't use it at all.{NOTE:もう役に立てない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.17,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:382670,384170}– Hongou.\N– Hm?{NOTE:—本郷。\\N—ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:27.47,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:384170,387470}I was surprised when I heard that you became a volleyball coach.{NOTE:驚いたぞ。御前がバレーのコーチを遣ってるとはな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.76,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:388550,391760}Heh. Well, I didn't have any experience in the field.{NOTE:いや。バレーの経験は全く無かったが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:34.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:391760,394560}But I thought I could make it with enough passion and team spirit.{NOTE:愛情を持って、一緒に遣っていけばと思ってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.27,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:394560,396270}You never change, do you?{NOTE:相変わらずだな、御前は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:396270,397060}Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.69,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:397060,398690}You're too naive.{NOTE:甘いよ、御前は。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.73,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:398690,400730}Volleyball isn't such an innocent, sweet thing.{NOTE:バレーはそんな甘っちょろいものじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.94,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:403520,405940}Your coaching is no good.{NOTE:御前のコーチじゃ駄目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.82,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:405940,407820}What? What do you mean "no good"?{NOTE:何？駄目とは何だ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.24,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:407820,409240}Calm down, Hongou.{NOTE:落ち着け、本郷。}
