Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.62,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:411110,412620}They have what it takes.{NOTE:良い素質を持っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.99,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:412620,414990}But you? You're no good.{NOTE:しかし、御前じゃ駄目だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.08,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:414990,417080}You can't help them grow.{NOTE:今以上には育ってられ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.00,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:417080,419000}But I could teach them so much more.{NOTE:俺なら出来るだな。}
