Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:41.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:638138,641680}But I'm confident I could accept that spike now.{NOTE:…XXの分かった今ならレシーブ出来る自信があるわ。}
