Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:51.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:646470,651480}That Inokuma guy has been all around the world, to places like the Soviet Union and Europe, right?{NOTE:その猪野熊と言うの人はずいぶん長い間ソ連やヨーロッパに行ってたそうだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:651480,652150}Yeah.{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:652150,655110}He seems to have been coaching volleyball for a long time in all sorts of places.{NOTE:色んな所でずっとバレーをやっていたらしいんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:57.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:655110,657400}But nobody knows anything specific.{NOTE:はっきり分からないんだって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:02.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:657400,662070}The only thing we know for sure is that\Nhe coached the North Korean college team.{NOTE:はっきりしてる事は北朝鮮の大学チームをコーチしていた事だけなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.49,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:662490,663490}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.87,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:663490,665870}Well, different countries have different volleyball.{NOTE:色んな国に色んなバレーがあるんだろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:673040,675840}True. Take Shellenina's Soviet team for example.{NOTE:あのシェレーニナのソ連チーム(X・のそう)だったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:22.14,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:677630,682140}There are so many amazing things in\hthe world that we do not know yet.{NOTE:世界には未だ未だ私達が知らない驚く様なことがいっぱいあるんだろうな。}
Comment: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:31.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:691770,691770}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:41.24,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:699400,701240}Studying during breaks?{NOTE:休み時間まで勉強？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.49,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:701240,702490}You're too much.{NOTE:凄いわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:702490,704280}Not really. I'm not studying.{NOTE:んん。そうじゃないんだけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.16,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:705580,707160}It's October already.{NOTE:もう十月ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.16,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:707160,710160}We need to take the high school entrance exams right after New Year's.{NOTE:年が変わったらすぐに高校の入学試験。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:710160,712080}So we can't stay relaxed, can we.{NOTE:のんびりしていられないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:712080,714080}I have to follow your lead, Kozue.{NOTE:私もこずえを見ながらなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:714080,715250}I told you I'm not studying.{NOTE:そうじゃないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.25,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:715250,716250}What about this?{NOTE:これよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:58.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:716250,718090}"The history of volleyball"?{NOTE:バレーボールの歴史？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.92,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:718090,720920}Why are you reading that book now?{NOTE:どうしたの？急にそんな本なんか読み出して。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:05.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:720920,725220}Nothing in particular, I just want to know more about volleyball.{NOTE:ん、どって事もないだけど。私もっとバレーの事を知りたくてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:08.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:725220,728180}I'd say history has nothing to do with us, though.{NOTE:歴史なんてあんまり関係無いみたいだけどな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:12.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:728180,732190}But is it really okay for us if we only practice and play matches?{NOTE:ね、私達ただ練習して、試合するだけで良いのかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:732190,734560}Shouldn't we know more about the sport we're playing?{NOTE:もっと知らなきゃいけない事があるんじゃないかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.52,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:734560,735520}I guess…{NOTE:そうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:19.48,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:735520,739480}Now that you mention it,\Nwe really do only play volleyball.{NOTE:そう言われれば、私達ただバレーをやってるだけね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.48,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:739480,741480}There are so many things I don't know.{NOTE:もっと見知らない事が多すぎるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:24.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:742650,744410}When was volleyball invented?{NOTE:バレーは何時頃できたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:26.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:744410,746410}Where did it start?{NOTE:誰がどこの国で？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.62,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:746410,748620}I suppose I'll have to study with you, if you insist so much.{NOTE:仕様が無いから私も勉強しようっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:748620,750790}But I never insisted on anything.{NOTE:あら、仕様が無いから、(XX・余計よ)。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:31.50,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:750790,751500}{NOTE:—ふふ。\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.54,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:751500,753540}{NOTE:—ははは。\\N—ふふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.83,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:753540,754830}Captain!{NOTE:キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.79,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:754830,756790}– Captain.\N– What's wrong, Kakko?{NOTE:—キャプテン。\\N—あら、どうしたの、カッコ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.84,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:756790,758840}This is no time for relaxing.{NOTE:あ、落ち着いた場合じゃないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:42.17,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:758840,762170}Naka and Okei want to quit the club.{NOTE:ナカやおケイ達がね、バレー部辞めるって言うのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:43.76,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:762170,763760}– Eh?\N– Eh?{NOTE:—え？\\N—え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:763760,765090}Quit?{NOTE:辞める？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:51.47,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:768390,771470}That's right. It's not an easy decision.{NOTE:そうなのよ。それは悩みの種なのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:55.06,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:771470,775060}I was planning to talk it over with Captain.{NOTE:キャプテンとはゆっくり相談しようと思ってたんだけどさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.61,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:775060,778610}We want to enter\NFujimi High School no matter what.{NOTE:私達さ、どうしても富士見高校へ入りたいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.53,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:778610,780530}We want to play volleyball at high school too.{NOTE:高校へ行ってもバレーをやりたいのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:04.36,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:780530,784360}But to do so we need to take a\hbreak and study for the exams.{NOTE:そのためにはね、今休んで受験勉強しなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:07.99,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:784360,787990}Captain and Midori are safe since they've got good grades.{NOTE:ん、それはキャプテンやみどりは成績が良いからいくでさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:14.79,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:787990,794790}But I'm not that good. I don't know if I can pass even if I try hard from now on. It's no joke.{NOTE:私なんか一番出来ない子。私今から頑張っても合格するかとか分かんないくらいだもんね。(XX・やん)成っちゃうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:18.79,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,{TIME:794790,798790}– Ofuku and Yukie said the same.\N– T-They did, huh?{NOTE:—おフクやゆきえだって辞めるって言ってたよ。\\N—そう。そう言ってたわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:802260,805590}Let's all meet after school and talk it through, okay?{NOTE:放課後皆で集まってもう一度話をしない？ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:805590,807430}Yeah. Good idea.{NOTE:ん、そうね。}
