Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:821190,823530}It can't be helped with the exams\Nright around the corner.{NOTE:仕方は無いわね、受験勉強じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.95,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:823530,826950}I'm also going to study for entrance exams.{NOTE:私だって受験勉強しなきゃいけないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:49.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:826950,829570}At any rate, I'll keep doing my best until graduation.{NOTE:私は兎に角卒業まで頑張るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:52.83,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:829570,832830}After all, we need to oversee\Nthe first and second years' practices too.{NOTE:だって、一年生、二年生の練習も見なきゃいけないもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:57.25,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:832830,837250}Then that makes Captain, Midori, and me the only seniors that are left.{NOTE:そうすると三年生で残るのは…キャプテンとみどりと私の三人ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.42,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:837250,839420}That's fine. Everyone, study hard.{NOTE:良いわよ。皆しっかり勉強してよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:03.05,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:839420,843050}I'm not going to high school, so I will take over your duties.{NOTE:私は進学しないんだから、皆の分に引き受けるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:06.63,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:843050,846630}Besides, I'd like to play volleyball all that I can before I graduate.{NOTE:それに、私卒業するまで思いっきりバレーをしておきたいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.51,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:846630,849510}After that I'll need to help my folks and won't get to play anymore.{NOTE:卒業したら内の手伝って出来なくなるんだもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.56,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:850930,853560}Why don't you form a team in your town?{NOTE:ね、町でチーム作ればいじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.68,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{TIME:853560,855680}I'll be too busy with the restaurant.{NOTE:忙しいのよ、食堂って。}
