Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:47.59,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:884130,887590}I guess you're right. I'm starting to feel a little lonely now.{NOTE:そう言う事かな？なんだか寂しく成っちゃったな、私。}
