Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.19,Default,Katori,0,0,0,,{TIME:905400,907190}Come on? Ah…{NOTE:ね、へへ…あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.49,Sign,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912740,915490}Teacher's office{NOTE:職員室	}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:20.67,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:918160,920670}Nakazawa, Fukuda, Ikezaki.{NOTE:中沢、福田、池崎。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.92,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:920670,923920}Ooki. Kudou. Katori.{NOTE:大木、くどう、かとり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.55,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:923920,925550}Ozawa.{NOTE:小沢。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.13,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:925550,928130}Those are all that want to quit?{NOTE:退部するのはこの七人だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:928130,929420}Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.51,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:929420,931510}Very well. Thank you.{NOTE:よし。分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.72,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:931510,932720}Ah, Ayuhara!{NOTE:あ、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:33.97,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:932720,933970}Wait a moment.{NOTE:ちょっと待ててくれんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.43,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:935260,936430}Why don't we go together?{NOTE:一緒に帰ろう。}
