Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:50.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:944980,950610}I'm not sure yet, but I think it'll be Hayakawa-san, Nakazawa-san, Kudou-san and Katori-san.{NOTE:まだ分かりませんが、早川さん、中沢さん、くどうさん、かとりさんはそうだと思います。}
