Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:06.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:962830,966040}It makes me wonder for how long\Ncan I play volleyball myself.{NOTE:私もいつまでバレーを続けられるかと思うと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:10.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:966630,970210}No matter the sport, it isn't easy to keep on with it.{NOTE:何のスポーツでも、それを続けていく事は容易い事じゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.97,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:970210,971970}It's a tough and difficult business.{NOTE:厳しく、難しい物だ。}
