Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:41.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360480,1361520}But, that's…{NOTE:でも、その…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:45.19,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361520,1365190}To prepare the representatives for the championship…{NOTE:選手権に備えて、代表選手の強化合宿は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:48.57,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365190,1368570}…there will be a training camp held for one month in Miyazaki, Kyūshū.{NOTE:九州の宮崎で一ヶ月にわたって行われる。}
